18699::$$$message_0176_0000_0000$$$::Let's prepare something we didn't have before: a new weapon.[lr]::
18700::$$$message_0176_0000_0001$$$::I'm sure Saber would benefit from a weapon other than Excalibur, and the more weapons I have, the better.::
18701::$$$message_0176_0001_0000$$$::"Shirou? What is it that you have in mind?"[lr]::
18702::$$$message_0176_0001_0001$$$::"Well, I was thinking of getting more weapons. This place was originally my old man's storehouse. We might be able to find something useful if we look around."::
18703::$$$message_0176_0002_0000$$$::"Something...useful?[lr]::
18704::$$$message_0176_0002_0001$$$::Yes, if we find any magecraft objects Kiritsugu used to use, they would certainly benefit you. His Mystic Code of choice was a gun, so you should be able to use that easily."::
18705::$$$message_0176_0003_0000$$$::A Mystic Code is a tool or armament mages use to empower or support their spellcasting.[lr]::
18706::$$$message_0176_0003_0001$$$::According to Saber, my old man's was a pistol.::
18707::$$$message_0176_0004_0000$$$::"Huh. That seems like a pretty dangerous thing to use, but I guess it's an effective weapon."[lr]::
18708::$$$message_0176_0004_0001$$$::"Yes. I will check here. You should look in the attic.[lr]::
18709::$$$message_0176_0004_0002$$$::If it is here, there should be a seal that suppresses its magical energy. Rather than detecting its magical energy, just search the entire area with a fine-tooth comb."::
18710::$$$message_0176_0005_0000$$$::"I can't find anything, Saber."[lr]::
18711::$$$message_0176_0005_0001$$$::"Me either. I cannot find a gun...or even a note that might indicate where it is stored."[lr]::
18712::$$$message_0176_0005_0002$$$::"I guess I'm not surprised. If the old man had left anything like that, I would've found it long ago."::
18713::$$$message_0176_0006_0000$$$::I feel defeated.[lr]::
18714::$$$message_0176_0006_0001$$$::Well, it didn't hurt to try. Now we just have to do our best with what we have, like we planned from the start.::

